k Life Week</h3><p class="sc-eLwHnm fPjVqe pf-44_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">National Work Life Week serves as a crucial reminder of the importance of prioritising work-life balance in today's hectic world. By raising awareness and promoting discussion around this topic, the campaign encourages employers and employees to evaluate their current practices and consider implementing changes to support a healthier balance.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-jrQzAO jIEVBe pf-46_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gIDmLj bESFPC pf-47_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hmjpVf IvCUC pf-48_ pf-heading-1-h3">Key facts and statistics</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-eGPXGI hfOvrX pf-50_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-51_ pf-text-1">According to a study by the Mental Health Foundation, work-related stress accounts for 37% of all work-related ill health cases and 45% of all working days lost due to ill health in the UK.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-53_ pf-text-1">Flexible working arrangements, such as remote work options or flexible hours, have been shown to increase job satisfaction, productivity, and employee retention rates.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-55_ pf-text-1">Research from the Harvard Business Review suggests that employees who feel they have a good work-life balance work 21% harder than those who don't.</li></ul></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gIDmLj bESFPC pf-57_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/mohdizzuanbinroslan_65f